data.description: Back on the market, buyer failed to close. Seller Financing available. 6% Rate with $25k down! Extensively renovated Layton residence notably close to Hill Air Force Base. Newer upgrades include central air conditioning, a thorough revamp of the plumbing system, and the replacement of the flooring with a combination of high-quality luxury vinyl plank (LVP) and plush carpeting. Additionally, the kitchen has been tastefully modernized, featuring a set of brand-new cabinets and elegant granite countertops. Call today to come and see this fantastic property!
